Barely a week after the abduction of six female pupils and two staff members of the Engravers College, Chikun Local Government Area of the State, Some gunmen have reportedly attacked the Government Technical Secondary School, Mararaban Kajuru in Kajuru Local Government Area of the state. The gunmen abducted the principal of the school. He was kidnapped around 1:00 am Thursday morning. The PPRO of the Kaduna State Police Command, DSP Yakubu Sabo was called to confirm the incident but did not reply text messages and calls to his phone. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .